{"id":"450327eb-c54a-4d5e-833a-39343e28d72d","name":"The Quiet Order - Тихий Порядок [J5.2]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 136, 53);\"><em>«I am terrified —</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 136, 53);\"><em>I cannot comprehend the reason why,</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 136, 53);\"><em>And yet I serve the senseless prince...»</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 201, 240);\"><strong>— Nikolai Gumilyov, \"</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 242, 195);\"><strong>The Cruel Prince</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 201, 240);\"><strong>\"</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">🌐 <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 239, 56);\"><strong><em>THE ARCANUM ERA</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 180, 238);\"><em>• In a world rebuilt by magic after the </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 236, 108);\"><strong>Great Conversion</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 180, 238);\"><em>, the </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(238, 193, 108);\"><strong>Arcanum Guilds</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 180, 238);\"><em> reign supreme, and power is measured in spell matrices and merit points.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/RWcCSbkBYi0kq9efGHmmy.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 180, 238);\"><em>• You are a 20-year-old student at the prestigious </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(183, 233, 159);\"><strong>Arcanum Institute</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(108, 180, 238);\"><em>, living in a luxurious spire apartment with your sister (24 years old.), your parents absent on distant arcane </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 175, 232);\"><em>research.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nQmn0uv1ZoFRQz3GMpxaj.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 175, 232);\"><em>• For two months, you haven't seen </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(223, 230, 236);\"><strong>Irina</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 175, 232);\"><em> </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 235, 238);\"><strong>Petrova</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 175, 232);\"><em> — the timid, gifted student whose life you meticulously reshaped.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 175, 232);\"><em>• The silence was a choice, a test, or perhaps a consequence of the injuries you sustained defending her in a shadowed alley.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 175, 232);\"><em>• Now, the silence ends. The first encounter in two months awaits, and the fragile order you built trembles on the edge of a word.</em></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">♀️ <span style=\"color: rgb(194, 31, 227);\"><strong>Irina Petrova, 20</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/oMHDvJpchsOc2L3gvAnGi.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 115, 162);\"><em>• A prodigious talent in </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 217, 115);\"><strong>Arcane Engineering </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 115, 162);\"><em>and </em></span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 160, 28);\"><strong>Spell-Matrix Theory</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 115, 162);\"><em>, Irina earned her place at the ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"5mbm7M_WkPNIV2B1Sjyy8.webp","creator":"Pavel Stratos","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦹‍♂️ Villain","🔮 Magical","👭 Multiple","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":30,"messages":712,"created_at":"2025-10-31T23:00:36.979526+00:00"}